      "text": "Doesn't matter."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.59,
      "end": 528.52,
      "text": "Maybe it's a time you take a piece of prosciutto and you whack him over the head."
    },
    {
      "start": 531.31,
      "end": 535.91,
      "text": "When I was little, you told me I should never have to squeeze love out of a man's heart."
    },
    {
      "start": 536.13,
      "end": 538.48,
      "text": "But if it doesn't come freely, I don't want it."
