    },
    {
      "start": 539.86,
      "end": 541.2,
      "text": "What else did I say?"
    },
    {
      "start": 541.78,
      "end": 546.63,
      "text": "That boys are stupido and that I can do anything better than they can."
    },
    {
      "start": 546.75,
      "end": 548.59,
      "text": "Ah, you see, I'm a wise woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.59,
      "end": 552.98,
      "text": "네, 그럼 프랑카 아이머 언니의 말부터 들어보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 553.36,
      "end": 554.48,
      "text": "It's good to cry."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.9,
      "end": 556.36,
